### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Start trip
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/trips/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "car-pi"
}

### Send moving location
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "car-pi",
  "timestamp": "2026-06-07T14:20:00Z",
  "lat": 57.7089,
  "lon": 11.9746,
  "speedKmh": 82,
  "heading": 142,
  "accuracyMeters": 8,
  "source": "simulated"
}

### Send stopped location
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "car-pi",
  "timestamp": "2026-06-07T14:25:00Z",
  "lat": 57.7101,
  "lon": 11.9758,
  "speedKmh": 0,
  "heading": 142,
  "accuracyMeters": 8,
  "source": "simulated"
}

### Current state
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/state

### Suggestion placeholder
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/suggest

### Stop trip
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/drive/trips/stop
